{"word":"H7049 - קָלַע - qâlaʻ - kaw-lah' - Carve","slug":"H7049","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">קָלַע</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>qâlaʻ"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>kaw-lah'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Carve"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E7;&#x05DC;&#x05E2; - qa&#x0302;la&#x201B;</b> - <i>kaw-lah'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>sling</i>; also to <i>carve</i> (as if a <i>circular</i> motion, or into <i>light</i> forms): - carve, sling (out)."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4734\">H4734</a>, <a href=\"#/H7053\">H7053</a>, <a href=\"#/H7055\">H7055</a>"}]}